description: [``botocore``] Release of feature needed for ECA-Endpoint settings. This allows customer to delete a field in endpoint settings by using --exact-settings flag in modify-endpoint api. This also displays default values for certain required fields of endpoint settings in describe-endpoint-settings api.
[``botocore``] Add support for Event Driven Workflows
[``botocore``] Added support for RSA 3072 SSL certificate import

[``botocore``] General availability for Amazon HealthLake. StartFHIRImportJob and StartFHIRExportJob APIs now require AWS KMS parameter. For more information, see the Amazon HealthLake Documentation https://docs.aws.amazon.com/healthlake/index.html.
[``botocore``] This update provides support for Well-Architected API users to mark answer choices as not applicable.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for the Amazon Lightsail object storage service, which allows you to create buckets and store objects.
